-- Yahoo Chairman says Microsoft never made a compelling offer
-- 
-- Fri Aug 1, 2008 1:59pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/08/01/businesspro-yahooo-msft-dc-idUSMAR16467520080801

 

 (Reuters) - Yahoo Inc ( YHOO.O ) Chairman Roy Bostock says 
there was never any doubt about the position of Yahoo board 
about its openness to doing a deal with Microsoft. 

  * Chairman says he cannot understand why Microsoft withdrew 
its full-scale merger offer  * Chairman says "there was never a compelling offer put on 
the table"